xyzc.ini: [DISPLAY]GEOMETRY=CXYZ
Rotations respect G5x,G92 offsets

xyzc_legacy.ini: [DISPLAY]GEOMETRY=!CXYZ
The '!' character selects legacy behavior
with rotations applied with respect to
machine zero position


demo gcode file:
[DISPLAY]OPEN_FILE=xyzc.ngc 
demonstrates C rotations with and
without G5x and G92 offsets

Usage:
1) F1 ---------- estop off
2) F2 ---------- machine on
3) Ctrl-Home --- Home All
4) R ----------- Run program
   when paused, S to continue
